source:
TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Quest Sync<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
The seasoned scavenger has one last favor to ask.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var> Schwierigkeitsanpassung<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
Der erfahrene Schatz<var 16 /var>sucher hat noch eine Bitte an dich.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_TODO_01<tab>Use the blunt knife at the designated locations to catch rock wrigglers.
TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the rock wrigglers to the quick-witted scavenger.
TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_NOVICESCAVENGER03505_000_000<tab>Not just pretty, but valuable, too! Thank you!
TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_010<tab>There is one last thing I would ask of you, if I may be so bold.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_010<tab>Ganz schön gefährlich das war, aber dank dir wir leben und haben sogar unsere Schätze!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_011<tab>We are now ready to return to Twine, but I am afraid that I picked up a rather nasty injury while fending off those beasts.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_011<tab>Gehen jetzt zurück nach Pfotenschlag. Kannst du bitte vorgehen und unserem Freund sagen, dass wir sind unterwegs?

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_012<tab>It is not serious, and should heal in time, but it will take a while for me to complete the return journey. I would be grateful if you could go ahead and let our friend know that we are on our way back. We will see you in Twine!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_012<tab>Von Angriff in Kelk verletzt ich bin. Nur ganz langsam ich gehe. Bestimmt schneller du bist.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_020<tab>So, did you find my fellow scavengers?
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_020<tab><var 08 E905 ((Reisende)) ((Reisender)) /var>! Meine Freunde gefunden du hast?!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_021<tab>I am so relieved! My reputation is safe! And also, my friends are not dead!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_021<tab>So ein Glück! Lebendig sie sind! Große Sorgen ich gemacht.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_022<tab>But one of them is injured, you say? I should make sure he at least reaches Twine before he keels over... Unfortunately, we Mord do not heal in the same way as Humes or Ronso, so their treatments will not work on us.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_022<tab>Aber einer verletzt ist?! Ich besser besorgen Medizin. Körper von Mordh ganz anders als Hume oder Ronso. Brauchen spezielle Medizin!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_023<tab>He will need freshly prepared ointment to seal the wound, made according to our traditional recipe. While I can get most of the ingredients here in Twine, I still need two plump, juicy rock wrigglers.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_023<tab>Ich weiß spezielles Rezept für Mordh-Medizin! Nur Klitzekleinigkeit ich noch brauche.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_024<tab>If you could go and catch them for me, I will take care of the rest!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_024<tab>Zwei <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8F2A030502 /var> du mir fängst, ja? Alles andere ich hier schon habe.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_025<tab>They like to hide in the crags, so try hooking them out with this knife. Time is of the essence, so please do not dilly or dally!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_025<tab><var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E8F2A030502 /var> in Rissen und Spalten von Felsen leben. Mit Messer du kratzen sie heraus! Hier, nimm, nimm!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_030<tab>Rock wriggler blood is very sticky, so we use them for ointments. But remember, you must never try to eat one, unless you like having your tongue stuck to the roof of your mouth!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_030<tab>Felsenwürmer gut für Medizin! Verkriechen tief in Felsspalten, aber mit Messer du bekommst heraus!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_040<tab>Thank you for passing on my message. It seems you have been rather busy in our absence!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_040<tab>Puh, endlich in Sicherheit. Danke, <var 08 E905 ((starke Fremde)) ((starker Fremder)) /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_NOVICESCAVENGER03505_000_041<tab>We would have arrived a lot sooner if he was not limping the whole way!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_NOVICESCAVENGER03505_000_041<tab>Ganz schön weit der Weg, wenn man humpelt!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_051<tab>Excellent! Once I've squeezed out their blood and mixed it with the other ingredients, the ointment will be ready!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_051<tab>Wunderprächtig! Muss ich nur noch zerquetschen und mischen mit anderen Zutaten. Fertig ist die Mordh-Medizin!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_052<tab>But before we leave, my friends wish to offer their thanks.
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_052<tab>Los, ihr zwei, bedankt euch! Und dann wir gehen.

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_053<tab>You were under no obligation to help us, but you did so without a thought for your own safety. We will never forget you!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_EXPERTSCAVENGER03505_000_053<tab>Danke, <var 08 E905 ((Fremde)) ((Fremder)) /var>! Ohne dich verloren wir waren. Gerettet du uns hast!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_NOVICESCAVENGER03505_000_054<tab>And the rest of Twine is sure to be impressed by our adventures! I am glad to be alive to tell the tale!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_NOVICESCAVENGER03505_000_054<tab>Ja, ja! Allen erzählen ich werde, was du für uns getan. Danke!

source: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_055<tab>Your deeds will live on in the stories we share with our children, and our children's children! Fare thee well!
target: TEXT_LUCKZG020_03505_MORDSCAVENGER03505_000_055<tab>Sehr geholfen du uns hast! <var 08 E905 ((Große Freundin)) ((Großer Freund)) /var> von Mordh du bist!
